#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:244
msgid ""
"This app uses Ubuntu Touch Online Accounts. Edit this only if the system "
"account did not expose the correct server address."
msgstr ""
"Denne app bruger Ubuntu Touch Online Accounts. Rediger kun dette, hvis "
"systemkontoen ikke oplyste den korrekte serveradresse."

