msgid "No Nextcloud account found"
msgstr "Ingen Nextcloud-konto fundet"

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:304
msgid ""
"Add a Nextcloud or ownCloud account in Ubuntu Touch System Settings > "
"Accounts, and allow %1 to use it. Then return here and select it."
msgstr "Legg til en Nextcloud- eller ownCloud-konto i Ubuntu Touch Systeminnstillinger > Kontoer, og tillat %1 å bruke den. Kom deretter tilbake hit og velg den."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:418
msgid "Verify selected account"
msgstr "Bekræft valgt konto"

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:418
msgid "Verifying account..."
msgstr "Bekræfter konto..."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:440
msgid "How to allow this account"
msgstr "Sådan tillades denne konto"

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:503
msgid "Selected %1. Verifying authorization..."
msgstr "Valgte %1. Bekræfter godkendelse..."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:521
msgid "Saved account selected. Verify again if needed."
msgstr "Gemt konto valgt. Bekræft igen om nødvendigt."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:565
msgid "Select an account first."
msgstr "Vælg først en konto."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:570
#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:672
msgid "Verifying Online Accounts authorization..."
msgstr "Bekræfter Online Accounts-godkendelse..."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:586
msgid ""
"Authorization succeeded, but the Ubuntu Touch account did not expose a "
"server address for %1."
msgstr ""
"Godkendelsen lykkedes, men Ubuntu Touch-kontoen oplyste ikke en "
"serveradresse for %1."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:588
msgid ""
"Authorization succeeded for %1. Credentials are available to the app, but "
"were not displayed or stored."
msgstr ""
"Godkendelsen lykkedes for %1. Loginoplysninger er tilgængelige for appen, "
"men blev hverken vist eller gemt."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:611
msgid ""
"Ubuntu Touch Online Accounts did not allow %1 to use this account yet. Check "
"that %1 is enabled for this account in System Settings > Accounts, then "
"return here."
msgstr "Ubuntu Touch Nettkontoer har ikke gitt %1 tilgang til denne kontoen ennå. Sjekk at %1 er aktivert for denne kontoen i Systeminnstillinger > Kontoer, og gå deretter tilbake hit."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:614
#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountSessionAdapter.qml:163
msgid "Authorization was canceled."
msgstr "Autorisasjonen ble avbrutt."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:617
msgid ""
"Authorization failed. If the system did not show an Online Accounts prompt, "
"open System Settings > Accounts and allow %1 for this account, then try "
"again."
msgstr "Autorisasjon mislyktes. Hvis systemet ikke viste en Nettkontoer-forespørsel, åpne Systeminnstillinger > Kontoer og tillat %1 for denne kontoen, og prøv igjen."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:633
msgid ""
"Open Ubuntu Touch System Settings manually, go to Accounts, add a Nextcloud "
"or ownCloud account, then return to %1 and select it."
msgstr ""
"Åbn Ubuntu Touch Systemindstillinger manuelt, gå til Konti, tilføj en "
"Nextcloud- eller ownCloud-konto, og vend tilbage til %1 for at vælge den."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:640
msgid ""
"Open Ubuntu Touch System Settings manually, go to Accounts, select %1, allow "
"%2 for that account, then return here. %2 will verify it automatically."
msgstr ""
"Åbn Ubuntu Touch Systemindstillinger manuelt, gå til Konti, vælg %1, tillad "
"%2 for kontoen, og vend tilbage hertil. %2 bekræfter automatisk."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:644
msgid ""
"Open Ubuntu Touch System Settings manually, go to Accounts, select the "
"Nextcloud account, allow %1 for that account, then return here. %1 will "
"verify it automatically."
msgstr ""
"Åbn Ubuntu Touch Systemindstillinger manuelt, gå til Konti, vælg Nextcloud-"
"kontoen, tillad %1 for den konto, og vend tilbage hertil. %1 bekræfter "
"automatisk."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:697
#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:725
msgid "No account selected"
msgstr "Ingen konto valgt"

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountPage.qml:708
msgid "The selected Ubuntu Touch account did not expose a server address."
msgstr "Den valgte Ubuntu Touch-konto oplyste ikke en serveradresse."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountSessionAdapter.qml:63
msgid "Desktop test credentials are incomplete."
msgstr "Desktop test credentials are incomplete."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountSessionAdapter.qml:82
msgid ""
"No account selected. Open Account first and authorize a Nextcloud account."
msgstr "No account selected. Open Account first and authorize a Nextcloud account."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountSessionAdapter.qml:88
msgid "No server URL configured. Open Account and authorize the OS account."
msgstr "No server URL configured. Open Account and authorize the OS account."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountSessionAdapter.qml:104
msgid "Waiting for Online Accounts..."
msgstr "Venter på Online Accounts..."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountSessionAdapter.qml:110
msgid ""
"Selected Online Accounts service was not found. Open Account and verify the "
"account again."
msgstr "Selected Online Accounts service was not found. Open Account and verify the account again."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountSessionAdapter.qml:161
msgid ""
"This app is no longer allowed to use this account. Open System Settings > "
"Accounts, allow it again, then try again."
msgstr "Denne appen har ikke lenger tillatelse til å bruke denne kontoen. Åpne Systeminnstillinger > Kontoer, tillat den igjen, og prøv på nytt."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountSessionAdapter.qml:165
msgid "Authentication failed. Open Account and verify the account again."
msgstr "Autentisering mislyktes. Åpne Konto og verifiser kontoen på nytt."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/AccountSessionAdapter.qml:174
msgid ""
"Authentication succeeded, but the required Online Accounts credentials were "
"not available."
msgstr "Authentication succeeded, but the required Online Accounts credentials were not available."

#: vendor/NextCommon/qml/NextCommon/LanguagePage.qml:11
msgid ""
"Some translations are AI-assisted and not fully reviewed. You can help "
"improve translations in the project repository."
msgstr "Noen oversettelser er KI-assistert og ikke fullt gjennomgatt. Du kan hjelpe til med a forbedre dem i prosjektets repository."

